column5: Hey all, I'm trying to find the page for the fishing tournament.  I have the leaderboard link, but I need to add a fish for our team and can't find the link for that page...can someone please post it here for me...  Thanks Maureen
I think it's one thing that hasn't been restored yet Maureen. I'm still waiting to give Mike my 31 1/2" Wally for team 5!

You know, I had completely forgot about the tourney. I had MuskyJohn(jigs) take over the reins for me, but now he does not seem to be around( some kinda dustup happened on the board a month or so ago, I think). I don't have any links to anything now. And with the demise of the gallery where all the previous entries were uploaded, well...........................  Maybe try this anew starting in february again.
I think it's all a conspiracy 'cause team 5 is kickin @$$ !
I wouldn't know.  I don't believe it for a minute!!!  But I don't know.

Here's the latest link I got Maureen.  http://www.ofntournament.com/tourney.htm  Only thing is, I don't think it is right. Team 5 has my NGL trout in their line. It hasn't been updated for quite some time either.  Riiiiick, oh Riiiiiick! What's scoop bud?

Thanks guys, I know one link is working as I recieved confirmation of an entry from a team member, guess I'll have to get him to give me the link he used and I'll pass it on here.  As for Team 5 kicking a$$, keep dreaming Wayne, as that's all you've got  Maureen
My season is pretty much done and I didn't make any contributions to my team (Team 5).  I guess I'll have to start planning for next year's tourney...  Mike
That sucks ... I carried my camera and OFC Cap and tapemeasure EVERYWHERE ... for nuthin ?  And Team 7 had it wrapped up
Thanks for the post camillj ...  Scratch that...I see someone stole your nuts and replaced them with a squirrel.
Ok, it was never lost, and here is the link for the tournament, courtesy of my team mate Camillj  http://www.ofntournament.com/  Thanks John  Maureen
So if I read it right,there is a tie?
Only 15 days to go...can't even find our Team rep to give the entry too...  31.5 " Wally. Dano has the tape measure shot as well if anyone disputes it's length.
Nice entry for our team, Wayne!  Mike
If we get it entered and if this things still a go. BIGFISH...what's the news?
wayne i emailed Mike a 31" eye last month,   he never gave me a "corfirmation" email like he did with other entries that i sent him earlier on this season
Just dug thru my old stuff and found the email address [emailÂ protected] so I've sent it to Mike there. Hopefully the tourney is still on track.  Wayne
